name: Diving Gymnastics
description:
HOW TO PLAY:
Dive like the graceful swan you are, then swim through the five Olympic rings before emerging victoriously from the water.

CONTROLS:
Space / Up Arrow to jump / propel forward
Left / Right Arrow to rotate
Esc to Reset

Diving Gymnastics was made for the NYU Game Center's Prototype Studio course, with the theme of "Licensed Game: The Olympics."
